OL,3,CTheatre leads way with dementia-
OL,4,Cfriendly performance of hit comedy show
OL,6,FA theatre leading the way by providing
OL,7,Fspecially adapted dementia friendly
OL,8,Fperformances of a hit show.
OL,10,FThe Lowry in Salford created a
OL,11,F60minute version of the acclaimed
OL,12,Fcomedy tribute Eric and Ern, as part
OL,13,Fof a run celebrating the centenary of
OL,14,FBritish comedy legends Eric Morecambe
OL,15,Fand Ernie Wise.
OL,17,FThe adapted shows offer audiences
OL,18,Fliving with dementia and their
OL,19,Ffamilies, friends, and carers a chance
OL,20,Fto experience live theatre in a
OL,21,Fsupportive and relaxed environment.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G1/6
