CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F396A1774523168
OL,3,CTheatre leads way with dementia-
OL,4,Cfriendly performance of hit comedy show
OL,6,FAdjustments include a shortened
OL,7,Fruntime, reduced sudden lighting and
OL,8,Fsound effects, and low house lights
OL,9,Fkept on throughout rather than full
OL,10,Fdarkness.
OL,12,FThe Lowry said audience members are
OL,13,Falso free to come and go from the
OL,14,Fauditorium as needed, while a quiet
OL,15,Fspace will be available for anyone
OL,16,Fseeking a break.
OL,18,FClear signage and additional staff are
OL,19,Falso on hand throughout the adapted
OL,20,Fperformance.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/6
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
