PN,39603
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F396A1774523168
OL,3,CTheatre leads way with dementia-
OL,4,Cfriendly performance of hit comedy show
OL,6,FAge UK Salford and Trafford have
OL,7,Ftrained staff to support people living
OL,8,Fwith dementia.
OL,10,FSteve Cowton, Head of Theatres at The
OL,11,FLowry, said: "We want everyone to feel
OL,12,Fat home at The Lowry, and we're proud
OL,13,Fto be presenting this Dementia-
OL,14,Ffriendly performance.
OL,16,F"Experiencing live theatre brings so
OL,17,Fmuch joy, and we want people to be
OL,18,Fable to continue to enjoy it long into
OL,19,Ftheir lives.
OL,26,@sD@NOUxD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G3/6
