PN,39604
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F396A1774523168
OL,3,CTheatre leads way with dementia-
OL,4,Cfriendly performance of hit comedy show
OL,6,F"Through consultation and feedback, we
OL,7,Fknow there is a real demand for
OL,8,Fdementia-friendly theatre
OL,9,Fperformances."
OL,11,FHe also praised the production team
OL,12,Ffor their collaboration, adding:
OL,13,F"They've created a 60minute version
OL,14,Fthat keeps all the classic comedy
OL,15,Fsketches people know and love, and the
OL,16,Ftechnical teams have minimised sudden
OL,17,Fscene changes and effects to keep the
OL,18,Fperformance as relaxed and comfortable
OL,19,Fas possible."
OL,26,@nD@AOUqD@NO]uD@AOU{D@MO]
