PN,39605
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F396A1774523168
OL,3,CTheatre leads way with dementia-
OL,4,Cfriendly performance of hit comedy show
OL,6,FStarring Olivier-nominated duo Ian
OL,7,FAshpitel and Jonty Stephens, 'Eric and
OL,8,FErn' pays tribute to Morecambe and
OL,9,FWise's comedy that made them household
OL,10,Fnames.
OL,12,FThe production forms part of a wider
OL,13,Fprogramme of celebrations marking what
OL,14,Fwould have been Eric and Ernie's joint
OL,15,F100th birthdays in 2026.
OL,17,FEric and Ern is here at Lowry from
OL,18,FTuesday 24 March Saturday 28 March and
OL,19,Fforms part of a series of celebratory
OL,20,Fperformances.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G5/6
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
