OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F396A1774523168
OL,3,CTheatre leads way with dementia-
OL,4,Cfriendly performance of hit comedy show
OL,6,FThe show goes onto the Garrick Theatre
OL,7,Fin London's West End, and Morecambe
OL,8,FWinter Gardens, and later this year
OL,9,Fthey also visit Waterside Arts Centre
OL,10,Fin Sale, Victoria Wood Theatre in
OL,11,FBowness-on-Windermere, Stockport Plaza
OL,12,Fand Lowther Pavilion in St Annes.
OL,14,FWant more on the issues affecting the
OL,15,FNorth? Our podcast, From the North
OL,16,Fanswers the questions that matter to
OL,17,Four region.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G6/6
